                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000402-78-off427 t18000402-78-cd428"></join>, a linen cloth, value 2d. and seventeen pounds of butter, value 17s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18000402-78-victim641" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Brooks
                  <interp inst="t18000402-78-victim641" type="surname" value="Brooks"></interp>
